data.description: Welcome to 140 Parker Street! This charming 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom house is now available for sale. Situated on a large lot, this property offers ample space and a variety of features that will surely catch your attention. Step inside and be greeted by the beautiful custom trim work and built-ins that add a touch of elegance to this home. The well-designed layout includes an office space, perfect for those who work remotely or need a quiet place for study. Enjoy the coastal lifestyle with a community sound beach access just a short distance away. For those seeking entertainment options, this property is conveniently located near the waterpark, providing endless fun for the whole family. Additionally, the Wright Memorial Bridge is in close proximity, making it an easy commute to Kitty Hawk beaches. Relax and unwind on the screened porch or soak up the sun on the spacious sun deck. The fenced yard offers the chance for your pets and children to play freely and safely. There is a 20x30 detached metal garage onsite with its own fuse box and electrical. With 2112 square feet of living space in the main house, there is plenty of room for everyone to spread out comfortably. The bedrooms are well-appointed and offer a peaceful retreat at the end of each day. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to own a wonderful home in a desirable location. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and make 140 Parker Street your new address!
